15,01 %%%----------------------------------------------------------------------%%%  
15,01 |  what's new in this version?                                             |  
15,01 %%%----------------------------------------------------------------------%%%  

15,01 Release Notes:                                                                

15,01 At last I again have time to work on Empathy! Developing Empathy was without  
15,01 a doubt one of the best experiences I've ever had in the bbs/art scene.  It's  

15,01 been so much fun relearning and rediscovering my coding past and just getting 
15,01 back into this whole realm that was such an important part of all of our      
15,01 teenage years.  Time is incredibly hard to come by for me these days (I now    

15,01 am a Philosophy, Mathematics, & Computer Science triple major at the Univ.    
15,01 of Texas at Austin) and working like crazy, so I must apologize for the time  
15,01 its taken me to even get this early beta of the new Empathy out.  I will do    

15,01 my very best to continue development in a much more timely fashion and thank  
15,01 you all so much for your input and patience.                                  

15,01 Next I will do my best to list what is new in this release.  Most of these    
15,01 have been requested by users; I will credit the requester in parenthesis      
15,01 where appropriate (Thank you testers!).                                       

15,01 New in this beta (12/30/2002):

15,01  Bug fixes:                                                                   

15,01  [x] Fixed cosmetic saving blue line text input bug. Thanks!                  
15,01  [x] Empathy now assumes that you wish to use available XMS instead of        
15,01      demanding 4megs and then allowing you to specify if it should fight for  
15,01      what's left in an allocation failure. This means no more "/small"         

15,01      command for everyone with an NT/XP based system. "/small" has been       
15,01      phased out and its equivalence in XMS allocation is assumed.             
15,01  [x] Fixed ASCII/Text saving bug. ASCII text files saved in Empathy now       
15,01      display accurately in standard text editors (req: radman).               
15,01  [x] New fast direct screen input/output routines; fixed retrace bug.         
15,01  [x] Fixed SAUCE loading bug!! (req: tasmaniac/radman).                       
15,01  [x] Fixed SAUCE saving bug!! (found and fixed on 12/03/02 4:23am).           
15,01                                                                               
15,01  [x] Alt+A screen now displays correct XBiN/ADF palette for attribute         
15,01      selection (req: radman).                                                 
15,01  [x] Excess lines in save fixed via Alt+Q (see below). (req: radman).         
15,01  [x] Added Alt+> & Alt+< confirmation. Not really a bug, I will double list.  
15,01      (req: radman; Note: > and < denote right and left arrows, not carats)    
15,01                                                                               
15,01  New Features / Commands:                                                     
